{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_support", "channel": "cs_representatives", "user": "rachel_lee", "message": "Team, I've received a few inquiries about the new software update. Please make sure to familiarize yourselves with the latest changes so we can continue to provide excellent service to our patients.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "executive_board", "channel": "strategy_planning", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "We need to discuss our upcoming budget allocation for the next quarter. I'd like everyone to come prepared with their department requirements for our meeting next week.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_support", "channel": "cs_representatives", "user": "mike_smith", "message": "Noted, Rachel. I'll make sure to go through the software update details. Thanks for the heads up!", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "executive_board", "channel": "strategy_planning", "user": "rachel_lee", "message": "Understood, Jane. I'll have the customer support department's budget requirements ready for our meeting.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_support", "channel": "cs_representatives", "user": "rachel_lee", "message": "Also, there's a customer service training session scheduled for next Monday. Please make sure everyone attends, it's mandatory.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "executive_board", "channel": "strategy_planning", "user": "jane_doe", "message": "We've received positive feedback from our recent customer satisfaction survey. Good job, everyone. Let's keep prioritizing our customer's needs and improving our services.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "customer_support", "channel": "cs_representatives", "user": "rachel_lee", "message": "As we approach the end of the year, I wanted to take a moment to acknowledge the hard work and dedication of our team. Specifically, I want to congratulate the five members of our team who received promotions in 2024. Two were promoted to senior representative roles, two to team lead positions, and one to quality assurance specialist. These promotions were based on their outstanding performance metrics, tenure, and the leadership they demonstrated.", "create_at": 1640995200000}}
